K12D0779=D1049_H0721:128b-0: @128b dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12D0779=D1049_H0721:128b-1: dkon mchog gsum gyi rten la sngags 'di lan re
K12D0779=D1049_H0721:128b-2: brjod cing brkyang phyag re byas te phyag gsum byas
K12D0779=D1049_H0721:128b-3: na sde snod gsum bros [?] pa dang /
K12D0779=D1049_H0721:129a-2: nyi ma re re phyag gsum gsum byas na tshe
K12D0779=D1049_H0721:129a-3: 'di nyid la mthong pa'i lam gyi ye shes kyi
K12D0779=D1049_H0721:129a-5: de ma thob kyi bar du mi dang /
K12D0779=D1049_H0721:129a-8: nad rims kyi gnod pa 'byung bar mi 'gyur ro //
K12D0779=D1049_H0721:129a-9: aom na mo manydzu shri ye /
K12D0779=D1049_H0721:129a-11: na ma aatta ma shri ye sv'ah'a /
